## âœ¨ Key Features Demonstrated in Prototype

[cite_start]Our simplest version includes the following working features[cite: 40, 43, 44]:
1.  [cite_start]**Real-Time Empathetic Chat:** Natural language conversation interface powered by Gemini 1.5 Pro[cite: 43].
2.  [cite_start]**Mood & Sentiment Detection:** Analysis of user text to infer mood and tailor the response[cite: 40].
3.  [cite_start]**Automated Journaling:** The AI automatically logs key emotional insights and progress to the database[cite: 44, 45].
